description: This file defines a data model for movie scripts using Pydantic, sets up an agent with a deepinfra model to generate movie scripts, and includes code to print a response based on a prompt.

classes.name: MovieScript
classes.description: A Pydantic model representing the structure of a movie script, including setting, ending, genre, name, characters, and storyline.

methods.name: agent.print_response
methods.description: Method to print the response content generated by the agent.
